  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective, non-randomized, observational study conducted in the United States.Up
      to sixty (60) subjects will be enrolled. The purpose of the study is to evaluate long-term
      utility and usability of Dexcom G4 Continuous Glucose Monitoring (CGM) System. Subjects will
      be followed monthly over a period of one year.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
